utility: Los Angeles Department of Water & Power
description:
&#x;fffdThis optional rate is available to Rate A customers and is designed to support new customer generation and to encourage clean onsite generation.
 
&#x;fffdRate C is available to customers whose total Rated Generation Capacity located at a customer facility is less than 25 percent of the Maximum Coincident Demand and less than 1 MW.
 
&#x;fffdTo qualify for this rate, each customer on-site generation unit shall have been installed and/or converted on/after January 1, 2001 to emit no more than 0.5 pounds/MWH of nitrous oxides. Such emission limit must be maintained to continue to qualify. Verification as the Department determines shall be provided.
name: Subtransmission (34.5 kV) CG-3(C)
